name: [r.u.s.h.] Parkour Prototype 1
description: Here is my blocktober level design project. 6 tracks made by me using an fps controller built by Josh Peters. The 2d hand and leg animation controller, tracks, & checkpoints were made by me. In the future I might continue to work on this and make it a sequel to my game Vacancy Unlimited. I hope you enjoy these tracks and they encourage you to also make something for blocktober next year! Crush my times and have fun everyone.
